com.odesk.agora.mercury.publisher

Class TopicPublisher

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.odesk.agora.mercury.publisher.TopicPublisher

  • public class TopicPublisher
extends Object
    Created by Dmitry Solovyov on 11/23/2015.

    Publisher for specific Mercury topic. The instances should be obtained via TopicPublishersFactory.getPublisherForTopic(String). Additionally, Agora core provides an ability to inject the publishers with @Inject @Named("YourTopicName") TopicPublisher topicPublisher;.

    The publisher is thread-safe, so one should use the same instance to construct and publish the messages from different threads simultaneously.

    It is the main public API point (facade) at publisher side.

      • messageWithThriftPayload

        public <T> TopicPublisher.MessageToPublish messageWithThriftPayload(T value)
        Construct a message with Thrift-based payload to be automatically serialized to "application/x-thrift+json" contentType. Default thrift serializer for TBase is registered in MercurySerializers automatically by Agora core. User can register a custom thrift serializer for T class to override the default one. Shorthand for messageWithObjectPayload(value, "application/x-thrift+json").
